 x = \frac{a\alpha x_A + b\beta x_B + c\gamma x_C}{a\alpha+b\beta+c\gamma} \qquad y = \frac{a\alpha y_A + b\beta y_B + c\gamma y_C}{a\alpha+b\beta+c\gamma} 
